name: CS Loves Me - Baby Blue
description:
Logo Dimensions(if outlined in a box) - 12" long, 10" wide
Logo is on the front of the shirt.

S - 26.5" long, 18" wide
M - 28" long, 19.5" wide
L - 29" long, 22" wide
XL - 30" long, 23" wide

Width is measured across the chest from one mid-armpit to the other.
Length is measured from the seam connecting the shoulder/neck, down to the very bottom of the shirt.
Shirts do shrink when washed for the first time.
Refunds are not offered at this time.

Thank you for your support! =)
